{
  "id": "adv_main_01_06_09",
  "title": "星見編2章4話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-3d",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_studio-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（東京でのダンスレッスン当日）\n（週に二回しか受けられない、貴重なレッスンだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Dance lesson day in Tokyo.）\n（This is an invaluable lesson that only takes place twice a week.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.2666666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "体の軸がぶれてます、川咲さん！\nだから足がもつれるんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your core isn’t aligned correctly‚ Kawasaki-san!\nThat’s why your feet get tangled up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　ごめん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right! My bad!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.966666666666663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん、テンポ速いよ！\n焦らなくて大丈夫！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa-chan‚ slow down your tempo!\nNo need to rush!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.125759673118585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.992426339785258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（みんな、いつにも増して気合の入り方が違うのは）\n（怜の事情を聞いたからだろう。だが――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The group is more enthusiastic than ever.）\n（Probably because they heard about Rei’s situation. But――）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.92040817737581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "dancea",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-dancea.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-dancea001.m4a",
      "text": "最後はみんな、センターに移動！　フィニッシュ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ everyone to the center! And finish!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.92040817737581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "きゃっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eek!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.95086162090303,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3.197442310920451e-11,
          "startTime": 29.950861620903062
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 32.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "……今のは兵藤さんが足下を気にし過ぎて\nみんなとの距離感を間違えてたからだと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hyodo-san‚ I think you messed up how far you were from the rest of us\nbecause you were too focused on the position of your feet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "でも……移動場所、見ないとわからない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… I need to see where I’m going.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "体に覚えさせるんですよ\n何度も、何度も、何度も繰り返して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You need to know instinctually\nby repeating it over and over again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "下ばかり見てるアイドルなんていません\n兵藤さんはアイドルになりたいんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No idol is always looking at their feet.\nDo you want to be an idol‚ Hyodo-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "それは……そう、だけど……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I do… but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "あ…………\n……ごめんなさい。言い過ぎました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh…\nSorry. That was mean of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "悪いの……私、だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… It’s my fault.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（怜はダンスに真剣だからこそ厳しい）\n（でもさくら達は指導を受け止めようと萎縮しているな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Rei is strict because she’s serious about dancing‚）\n（But the other members are intimidated by Rei's guidance…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.81277228705585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（グランプリの優勝という、向いている方向は同じ）\n（だけど、まだ歩調は噛み合っていないか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（They’re all working towards winning the Grand Prix‚）\n（but they’re still not quite on the same page yet.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "dancea",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-dancea.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-dancea002.m4a",
      "text": "……一旦休憩を挟みましょうか\n再開は十分後に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…….Let’s take a short break.\nWe’ll start again in 10 minutes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "わかりました\n……私、ちょっと顔洗ってきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright.\n……I’ll go wash my face real quick.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3066.666666666663,
          "startTime": 92.03333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……雫、あまり思い詰めなくても大丈夫\n前よりもグッと動きはよくなってるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s best not to overthink it‚ Shizuku.\nYour movements have improved a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "でも……言ってること、間違って、ない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… what she said isn’t wrong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。でもなんとかしなきゃって思えば思うほど\n焦って手足は動かなくなる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "True. But the more you think you have to do it perfectly‚\nthe more you’ll rush and make a misstep.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "だから『思い詰めなくていい』んだ\nそれくらいでちょうどいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why it’s best not to overthink it.\nJust keep it in the back of your mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くん……\nちょっといい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}…\nCan I talk to you for a sec?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……ちょっと電話してくる\nみんなはそのまま休憩しててくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m gonna go make a phone call.\nYou guys just keep resting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 126.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 126.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "どうした？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s the matter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "トイレの方で少し、ね\n行った方がいいと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Over at the bathroom.\nI think you should go check.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 133.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 133.86666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "何をそんなに焦ってるんだい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’re you so impatient about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 137.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_09-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "別に焦ってなんて……ただ、井川さんに会ったら\n訊いてみたいって、ずっと思ってたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not impatient. I’ve wanted to ask Igawa-san\nfor a while now‚ ever since we met.",
        "id": ""
      },
